DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-04-03T03:30:00&endDate=2026-04-07T00:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nHAMMERSMITH & CITY LINE: Good Friday 3\, Saturday 4\, Easter Sunday 5 and Easter Monday 6 April\, no service on the entire line.
